paragraph: A photography studio that specializes in ethereal emotive images.
Dos place collodion is a process that dates back to the 1850s. It involves coating a metal plate with a light-sensitive mixture.
Tres place collodion is an amazing process that allows you to create, beautiful, one-of-a-kind photographs!
